### 测试爬虫API接口

# 首先需要登录获取token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取爬虫配置选项
GET http://localhost:3000/crawler/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 测试连接
POST http://localhost:3000/crawler/test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 开始爬取推荐音乐（10首）
POST http://localhost:3000/crawler/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "recommended",
  "limit": 10
}

### 获取爬取进度
GET http://localhost:3000/crawler/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 开始爬取热门音乐（20首）
POST http://localhost:3000/crawler/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "popular",
  "limit": 20
}

### 开始爬取最新音乐（15首）
POST http://localhost:3000/crawler/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "latest",
  "limit": 15
}

### 停止爬取
POST http://localhost:3000/crawler/stop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 重置爬取进度
POST http://localhost:3000/crawler/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取爬取统计信息
GET http://localhost:3000/crawler/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查看爬取后的歌曲列表
GET http://localhost:3000/songs?limit=50&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=DESC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 搜索爬取的歌曲
GET http://localhost:3000/songs?search=测试&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
